                    <h2 data-uuid="6e5aba7151db40c195387324c3dc5721">Wayfaring Stranger</h2>
                    <p class="source" data-uuid="a295d1b8bfb742e4a97705aa2459baec">This spiritual can be dated at least to the early 1800s, although scholars are not certain exactly how old it is. A well-known song, it has been recorded many times by many artists over the years. Here, the performer sings it in a traditional gospel style.</p>
