                        <p class="pullquote" data-uuid="5589d0f97a7c45eb97052652e1e6ceec">I am a poor, wayfaring stranger<br />
                            Traveling through this world of woe<br />
                            Yet there’s no trouble, toil, nor danger<br />
                            In that bright land to where I go<br />
                        </p>
